The paper discusses the design of robotic systems for warehouse automation, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses perception apparatus and planning and control approaches, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the competition aspect of the challenge, which involves system integration and optimization, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
